<h3>Show Notes:</h3>

<p>
	In this episode of the podcast, Dan and Bekah talk with Lucia Cercie, a
	Software Engineer at <a href="https://stepzen.com/">StepZen</a>, mom, and
	Arizona transplant, about the importance of having a growth-mindset, asking
	questions, and pair programming. We also talk about the power of community and
	feeling comfortable asking questions and asking for help. When she's not
	coding, Lucia likes to make her baby laugh.
</p>

